<section sectnbr = "7B">
<servcat sctnbr = "07" scnbr = "02">
<configtype typenbr = "1">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AHRAP70A7216010" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Pregled motora puhala
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Provjerite otpor između dva terminala motora puhala kako je prikazano.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Ako nema kontinuiteta, zamijenite motor puhala.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A721013.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "42.472mm" ver = "01" gw = "219" gh = "104"/>
</figure>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Provjerite rad i struju motora puhala.
</ptxt>
</item>
<list2 type = "ordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Motor puhala (1) postavite u škripac s mekanim čeljustima.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Na motor puhala spojite akumulator kao što je prikazano.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Provjerite radi li motor puhala lagano bez buke.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Provjerite ampermetar prikazuje propisanu struju kada se izlaže naponu tijekom 1 minute.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Ako rezultat provjere ne odgovara propisanom, zamijenite motor puhala.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Specificirana struja motora puhala pri 12 V
</title>
<ptxt>
Maksimalno 16 A pri 20 – 25 &#176;C (68 – 77 &#176;F)
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A721039.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "44.463mm" ver = "01" gw = "206" gh = "110"/>
</figure>
</spec>
</item>
</list2>
</list1>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
